{"tid":2270883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五旬校巴司機認用傘打燈箱　判 12 個月感化","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:54:20.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7227ea2306f134603654a3097032134bc6250857","tid":2270883,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"去年 10 月《禁蒙面法》生效當日，大批市民上街遊行反對，期間一名 55 歲校巴司機被指在皇后像廣場外的巴士站，揮傘打向燈箱。他早前承認一項企圖刑事毀壞罪，今（4 日）在東區裁判法院被判 12 個月感化。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官錢禮判刑時指，最大的求情是被告主動認罪，其感化及社會服務令報告正面，相信被告已得到很大的教訓，因此決定接納感化官建議，判處 12 個月感化。"},{"pid":"cf652c480827cee52ab8150c96fbe02dbed73909","tid":2270883,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-5-%E5%8F%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E4%BA%94%E6%97%AC%E6%A0%A1%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%AA%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%82%98%E6%89%93%E7%87%88%E7%AE%B1-%E5%88%A4-12-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%25AE%25B1-%25E5%2588%25A4-12-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=c10f3ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%25AE%25B1-%25E5%2588%25A4-12-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%2F&h=4aff4047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/